<td style="border-width: 2px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; border-right: none; border-left: none; background-color: #eef0f8;" valign="middle">
<p>Si la altura de evacuación excede los 50 m.(6)</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr valign="top">
<td style="border-width: 2px; border-color: #000000; border-style: solid; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-left: none;" valign="middle">
